## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant insights from non-English publications. Additionally, the dynamic nature of hypercompetitive markets means that strategies may evolve rapidly, and the information presented may become outdated quickly.